Foot and mouth disease, Russia
--------------------------------
Information received on 1 Jul 2013 from Dr Evgeny Nepoklonov, Deputy Head, Federal Service for Veterinary and Phytosanitary Surveillance, Ministry of Agriculture, Moscow, Russia

Summary
Report type: Follow-up report No. 2
Date of start of the event: 3 Jun 2013
Date of pre-confirmation of the event: 8 Jun 2013
Report date: 1 Jul 2013
Date submitted to OIE: 1 Jul 2013
Reason for notification: Reoccurrence of a listed disease
Date of previous occurrence: 29 May 2013
Manifestation of disease: Clinical disease
Causal agent: Foot and mouth disease virus
Serotype: A
Nature of diagnosis: Suspicion, Clinical, Laboratory (basic), Laboratory (advanced), Necropsy
This event pertains to the whole country

New outbreaks (3)
