Epidemiology
Source of the outbreak(s) or origin of infection: Unknown or inconclusive

Epidemiological comments:
1. Outbreak in Amurskaya Oblast: The source of infection is being established. Epidemiological investigation is being conducted. Distance from the state border [with China] is 15 meters. Watering place is on the Amur River.
2. Outbreaks in Krasnodarskiy Kray: The source of infection is being established. Epidemiological investigation is being conducted.

Control measures
Measures applied: Quarantine, Movement control inside the country, Screening, Disinfection of infected premises/establishment(s), Modified stamping out
No vaccination
No treatment of affected animals

Measures to be applied: Vaccination in response to the outbreak (s)

Diagnostic test results [Summary; for detailed information, please go to the original report at the source URL]
Laboratory name and type:
1. FGBU "Federal Centre for Animal Health" (National laboratory): performed indirect fluorescent antibody (IFA) test, positive
2. FGBI "Federal Centre for Animal Health" (FGBI "ARRIAH") (OIE's Reference Laboratory): performed the following (positive) tests:
a. antigen (Ag) detection ELISA
b. complement fixation test (CFT)
c. nested RT-PCR
d. nucleotide sequencing
e. polymerase chain reaction (PCR)
f. reverse transcription - polymerase chain reaction
g. (RT-PCR)

